channel.title: I'm the only one that can get on my server
channel.description:
Hey people. I have a problem... I recently tried to make my server Non-Hamachi, so I followed Soul's TuT. But it isn't working... I've done it all right and the only way for me to get on is if I put the port as 0.0.0.0 or 127.0.0.1
Also, I can't Compile, I have downloaded JDK 6.0 update 13 (latest one) and if I try and Compile it says I don't have it.
Thanks -Conja (aka Conor)

item.title: I'm the only one that can get on my server
item.dc:creator: @Fat_Cookies Fat Cookies
item.description:
@Fat_Cookies wrote:

[quote=“powerknite7, post:5, topic:273978”][quote author=Fat Cookies link=topic=362022.msg2752068#msg2752068 date=1239978339]
You put the port as 43594 and the IP as 127.0.0.1
[/quote]
lol than only he wil be able to logg in lol[/quote]
FAIL

He puts his IP as 127.0.0.1 (the host) and everyone else uses his IP (e.g 255.255.255.255)

Think before you post
